div.p:
Take a quantite of Annis ſeeds, Kicoris, and Ellecampana roots;

                     •
                  ong pepper and Garlike, of each a like, with three Egges, and ſome butter, a quantity of malmeſie, and ſome ſtrong Ale mixt together; and make it warme, and ſo giue it him, and keepe him warme.
